import { Nav, Navbar } from "react-bootstrap"
import MyStyle from '../../styles/colorStyle';
const Sidebar = () => (
    <Navbar collapseOnSelect expand="lg" style={MyStyle.col_background} variant="dark">
        <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="responsive-navbar-nav" />
        <Navbar.Collapse id="responsive-navbar-nav">
            <Nav defaultActiveKey="/home" className="flex-column" style={MyStyle.col_border}>
                <Nav.Link style={MyStyle.col_border} href="/home">Active</Nav.Link>
                <Nav.Link style={MyStyle.col_border} eventKey="link-1">Link</Nav.Link>
                <Nav.Link style={MyStyle.col_border} eventKey="link-2">Link</Nav.Link>
                <Nav.Link style={MyStyle.col_border} eventKey="link-3">Disabled</Nav.Link>
            </Nav>
        </Navbar.Collapse>
    </Navbar>


)

export default Sidebar;
